
POST, PUT
/user_details/<user_name>
{

  "user_blob":<users description ie users profile descrption>,
  "user_picture_links": ["vrindavan/pic1","mountainview/pic2",....],
  "profile_links": ["facebook_link","youtube_page_link","linkedinlink"]
  "youtube_videos_links":["link1","link2"]

}

<json response is>
{

 "status":<status descrption goes here>
}

status code: 200, 401, 400
-------------------------------

GET
/user_details/<user_name>

<json response is>
{

  "user_blob":<users description ie users profile descrption>,
  "user_picture_links": ["vrindavan/pic1","mountainview/pic2",....],
  "profile_links": ["facebook_link","youtube_page_link","linkedinlink"]
  "youtube_videos_links":["link1","link2"]

}

<json response is>
{

 "status":<status descrption goes here>
}

status code: 200, 401

