POST
/login/<user_name>
{

  "password":<password>

}

status code: 200, 401

--------------------------------


POST
/change_password/<user_name>
{
  
  "oldpassword":<password>
  "newpassword":<password>
}

return:
status code: 200, 401

--------------------------------
POST
/logout/<user_name>
{

  "password":<password>

}

status code: 200, 401

